                        <div class="js-script-content-wrapper top-margin-script markdown-content">
                                                                                        <a href="https://github.com/knpuniversity/phpstorm/edit/master/knpu/refactoring.md" target="_blank" class="btn btn-default btn-circle pull-right js-tooltip" title="Edit on GitHub"><span class="fa fa-pencil"></span></a>
                                                                    <p>Ok back to work, let's finish up this <code>MovieController</code>. <code>Command+O</code>, <code>MovieController</code>,
and now we've got that file open.</p>
<p>We need to save the POST'ed movie to the database. Start with getting our entity manager
with <code>$em = $this-&gt;getDoctrine()-&gt;getManager();</code>. Then <code>$em-&gt;persist($movie);</code>, and
<code>$em-&gt;flush();</code>:</p>
