<p>Nice and simple!</p>
<p>While we're here, I'll copy the <code>getDoctrine()</code> line and paste it into <code>listAction()</code>
so we can make that work. Here we'll query for the movies with <code>$em -&gt;getRepository()</code>
and the first cool thing here is that... you guessed it! We get autocomplete on
this. Type the entity name, select the right one and hit tab:</p>
