<h2 id="refactoring-to-a-basecontroller">Refactoring to a BaseController <a class="headerlink" href="refactoring#refactoring-to-a-basecontroller" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>This shortcut is going to be useful in more than just this controller, so this is
the perfect time to create a <code>BaseController</code> for my whole project. Click the <code>Controller</code>
directory at the top of your IDE, and from there press <code>command+n</code>, select <code>Controller</code>
from the menu and name it <code>BaseController</code>. To start, remove that public function
and add <code>abstract</code> before the class:</p>
