	                            <div id="dsq-comment-text-2723165033" class="dsq-comment-text">
	                                <p>Yep, I do something similar - I use Refactor in PhpStorm... but I know it's not perfect (it never could be - there are some things that are just too dynamic for phpstorm to realize). I grep my code-base a lot to be completely sure when I make these changes. In this case, I would search for Twig instances by using:</p><p></p><pre><code><br>git grep '\.type'<br></code></pre><p></p><p>I wasn't familiar with the "Replace in Path" - that sounds very cool!</p><p>Cheers!</p>
