	                                <p>Hey Matt!</p><p>Yep, I know that error :). It means that there's a syntax error in the annotations above the samsCharacterName in your Movie entity - you might be missing a comma between your properties (e.g. @ORM\Column(name="sams_character_name", length=255).</p><p>Btw, I like your entity+property name :)</p><p>Cheers!</p>
